# One of these work - I'm not sure when and why ...

bindkey "[D" backward-word # Bind `Alt + Left Arrow` to move one word back
bindkey "[C" forward-word # Bind `Alt + Right Arrow` to move one word forward

bindkey "\e[1;3C" forward-word # Bind `Alt + Left Arrow` to move one word back
bindkey "\e[1;3D" backward-word # Bind `Alt + Right Arrow` to move one word forward
